    <section id="home-part5">
        <h2>Advancing Science through Open Collaboration</h2>
        <p>
            MetaROR advances science by making peer review transparent and accountable. Reviews receive DOIs, publicly crediting
            reviewers and integrating their contributions into the broader scholarly dialogue. This open approach accelerates
            knowledge dissemination and collaboration across the research community.
        </p>
        <ul class="advance-science-list">
            <li>
                {% include "./svg/phone.njk" %}
                <h3>Transparent feedback</h3>
                <p>
                    Peer review is transformed from a secretive process to an open, transparent activity, enhancing trust and
                    accountability in research.
                </p>
                <a href="">Discover more</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                {% include "./svg/route.njk" %}
